Short example of Example of manipulating a copy request using
clipboard events [1] and the HTML Editing API [2].

Online example: http://reggna.github.io/clipboard-stealer/clipboard-stealer.htm

This should work in IE, Chrome and Opera (>=15).

[1]: http://www.w3.org/TR/clipboard-apis/#beforecopy-event
[2]: https://dvcs.w3.org/hg/editing/raw-file/tip/editing.html#selection
